 discount is valid on the purchase of selected items and selected brands, excluding taxes, in U.S. Nordstrom stores and online at Nordstrom.com. Discount is off full price of eligible items. Online, prices are as marked; prices on product pages and in the app reflect the discount. In store, discount taken at register. Online, eligible products will be marked as Price Matched. Price Matched items are eligible for price adjustments within 14 days of shipment and may be applied to previous purchases as long as the item was not purchased at a Limited-Time Sale price. Does not include clearance or marked-down items. Not valid at Canada Nordstrom and Nordstrom Rack stores, U.S. Nordstrom Rack stores, Nordstromrack.com, Nordstrom.ca, Trunkclub.com or HauteLook. Cannot be applied to the purchase of Gift Cards, or payment on account, and cannot be redeemed for cash. While supply lasts. Terms are subject to change and offer is subject to end at any time without notice.